article.headline: Stephen F.Austin 76, Jarvis Christian 45
article.story: NACOGDOCHES, Texas -- Jordan Glynn scored 15 points and Dion Prewster added nine as Stephen F. Austin defeated Jarvis Christian 76-45 on Saturday night. Eddie Williams, Denzel Barnes and Amos Olytayo scored eight points each for the Lumberjacks (7-2). Gerneal White scored 11 points for Jarvis Christian (5-7), an NAIA school. A White 3-pointer got the Bulldogs within 48-38 with 9:20 remaining. But Stephen F. Austin scored the next 14 points during a span of 4:24 to put the game out of reach.
